metadata.name: Planet Parking 42
metadata.description:
I have been inspired by Damien Hirst's use of colours and have been experimenting with it to create this new artwork. This art plays with light and shadows, resulting in a stunning structure which looks like a parking lot for planet. Get ready to own a piece of the cosmos! 🪐🚀 

Don't miss out on the chance to add this unique piece to your collection! Get ready to launch into the cosmos and own a piece of my art. 🎨✨ 

#LimitedEdition #CosmicArt #GetReadyToBid #ArtLaunch #NewArtwork
